                                                  "content": "Great! I can see there's a `handle_errors` decorator available. Now let me examine the code_tools.py file to identify the functions that use try-catch blocks and update them to use the `@handle_errors` decorator instead.\n\nLooking at the code, I can see that:\n1. The `view` function has try-catch blocks (lines 29-83)\n2. The `patch_edit` function has a try-catch block (lines 165-326)\n\nLet me update these functions using the terminal:",
